    "46 For example, machine translations or chat bots that answer questions achieve both understanding and generation through multiple NLP tasks.",
    "It is not possible to remove some of the data after the model is trained.",
    "If a small part of the data needs to be removed (due to copyright or another reason, for example following an injunction), then the whole model may need to be retrained from the beginning or the output ''aligned''.",
    "The third case study focuses on computer vision.",
    "The developments in this field have been largely driven by industry uses, such as facial recognition or self-driving cars."
